..TEXT:
Before the descent of Christ into Hell no souls went
to Purgatory or Heaven: cf. ^Inf.~ IV, 63.  Ever since the
redemption the souls of the elect have reached Heaven through
Purgatory.  Virgil died in 19 A.D.
